description:
We are thrilled to bring back the fantastic rockabilly sounds of Aaron Lipp & The Slack Tones, with very special guests Rochester based, high energy americana folk rock act, A Girl Named Genny. For this show the Slack Tones will be joined by fiddle master, Duncan Wickel, to round out the 4 piece band. 

Doors: 7:30
Show: 8:00 till 1:00am. 
ONLY $5 ALL NIGHT! 

This special holiday kickoff event will feature an opening set from A Girl Named Genny, followed by a headlining 2 hour+ set from Aaron Lipp and the Slack Tones, followed by a late night set from A Girl Named Genny with special guests including Aaron Lipp! 

We will celebrate the oncoming season and the end of the harvest with fantastic music, drink specials, merryment and cheer! Prepare to dance the night away with some of the best talent upstate NY has to offer!
name: Aaron Lipp & Slacktones wsg A Girl Named Genny
